1f:T402,Internal evidence is coherent and clinically consistent. This is a specific configuration (4-hole, 63mm, 19.5mm width, right-sided) of a volar distal radial locking plate with multi-angle (0-15°) screw capability. The product appears to be a distinct implant SKU rather than a product family. Brand is missing (Meril listed as manufacturer but not as brand system owner). LPS likely means Locking Plate System. Double-column design and volar approach are standard for distal radius fracture fixation. Ti-6Al-7Nb is medically appropriate titanium alloy. Confidence reduced to 0.85 due to: (1) missing brand confirmation, (2) no external verification available, (3) ambiguity whether this specific configuration should be a standalone page or should merge into parent family as a variant. Recommend review to confirm: brand ownership, whether individual plate configurations warrant separate catalog pages vs. being variants within family page, and verification of 'Variabilis' as proprietary brand name vs. generic descriptor.1b:["$","$L1e",null,{"product":{"product_name":"Variabilis 2.4mm Multi-Angle Distal Radial Plate (4 holes, 63mm, Width 19.5mm, Right)","product_name_display":"Variabilis 2.4mm Multi-Angle Distal Radial Plate (4 holes, 63mm, Width 19.5mm, Right)","sku_code":"MT-PT7804063R","product_family":"Variabilis 2.4mm Distal Radial Plates","product_family_display":"Variabilis 2.4mm Distal Radial Plates","slug":"variabilis-2.4mm-multi-angle-distal-radial-plate-4-holes-63mm-width-19.5mm-right","images":[],"status":"published","live_visible":true,"brochure_url":"","seo_meta_title":"Variabilis 2.4mm Multi-Angle Distal Radial Plate (4 holes, 63mm, Width 19.5mm, Right) | Variabilis Multi-Angle Plates Distal Radial Plates - MedDevice Pro Telangana","seo_meta_description":"Variabilis 2.4mm LPS Multi-angle Double-Column Distal Radial Plate, Volar - 4 holes, 63mm, Width 19.5mm, Right. Multi-angle locking technology with 0-15 degr...","pack_size":"","size_variables":[],"creat